	(1, 7, 'Hospitality', 'hospitality', 'With the global hospitality industry experiencing rapid growth and increasing customer expectations, guest safety and operational continuity have become critical priorities for hotel operators who are strongly focused on protecting their brand reputation. At Xeluxe, we understand these challenges and go beyond compliance to deliver innovative and robust Fire & Life Safety solutions. ', '', 'uploads/images/14.jpg', '<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">With the global hospitality industry experiencing rapid growth and increasing customer expectations, guest safety and operational continuity have become critical priorities for hotel operators who are strongly focused on protecting their brand reputation. Hotels, resorts, serviced apartments, and entertainment facilities present unique fire safety challenges due to high occupancy levels, complex building layouts, mixed-use functions, and round-the-clock operations. </span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="