	(4, 1, 'Fire & Life Safety - Construction Supervision, Testing & Commissioning', 'fire-life-safety-construction-supervision-testing-commissioning', 'Xeluxe Consultants specializes in construction management across all MEP systems, offering testing and commissioning services for fire and life safety, HVAC, electrical, and plumbing systems. This systematic approach guarantees operational excellence, legal compliance, and the long-term resilience of buildings.', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-8">\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Construction Supervision</h3>\r\n<p>Xeluxe Consultants offers expert design and construction supervision services across the full spectrum of Fire &amp; Life Safety systems ensuring the success of projects throughout their lifecycle. Our expert range of fire engineers works collaboratively to deliver robust fire and life safety systems. By integrating these critical elements, we ensure design intent and code compliance while providing practical solutions that prioritize safety, efficiency, and sustainability.</p>\r\n<p>We partner with Project Management Consultants and Contractors as trusted advisors throughout the construction process, ensuring seamless multi-disciplinary coordination. We provide meticulous oversight to guarantee installations align with design specifications, industry standards, and regulatory requirements for various Fire and Life Safety systems. This approach ensures timely and successful project delivery.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="../uploads/images/29.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Testing and Commissioning of Building Systems</h3>\r\n<p>High-performing buildings depend on systems that are rigorously tested and commissioned to meet code requirements and the highest industry standards. Xeluxe Consultants specializes in construction management across all MEP systems, offering testing and commissioning services for fire and life safety, HVAC, electrical, and plumbing systems. This systematic approach guarantees operational excellence, legal compliance, and the long-term resilience of buildings</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="../uploads/images/37.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Our Specialized Services Include:</h3>\r\n<p>Fire Alarm &amp; Protection Systems - We ensure flawless design, installation, and commissioning of fire alarm, suppression, and integrated fire and life safety systems, safeguarding buildings and occupants.</p>\r\n<p>Integrated Building Systems for complex projects - &nbsp;we deliver cohesive integration of all MEP and fire safety systems, enabling seamless operation and enhanced functionality. From integrated testing of smoke management systems to various Fire Alarm integration requirements, our approach ensures interoperability and safety.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Commitment to Excellence</h3>\r\n<p>Xeluxe Consultants stands as a leader in delivering comprehensive Fire and Life Safety solutions for new construction projects. By leveraging our extensive experience and multidisciplinary expertise, we ensure that every aspect of a building&rsquo;s systems functions optimally, creating environments that are safe, efficient, and sustainable. Our dedication to innovation and excellence positions us as a trusted partner for successful project execution.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/38.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 7, 1, '2025-11-20 09:14:42', '2025-11-21 02:54:52'),
	(5, 1, 'Retrospective Assessment of Existing Facilities/ Risk Assessments', 'retrospective-assessment-of-existing-facilities-risk-assessments', 'We understand the need for a risk-based approach to be followed for existing buildings where prescriptive compliance may not be the norm always. Our Company has undertaken retrospective assessment of key assets within the region to ensure that the facility remains resilient and assure business continuity. \r\n', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">We understand the need for a risk-based approach to be followed for existing buildings where prescriptive compliance may not be the norm always. Our Company has undertaken retrospective assessment of key assets within the region to ensure that the facility remains resilient and assure business continuity. </span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Leveraging a blend of building plan assessments and onsite inspections, we offer a consolidated retrospective fire strategy for each facility. This comprehensive document compiles all pertinent fire safety data, facilitating improved planning for future alterations and operational decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">The strategy underscores alternative methods of compliance with local or international codes, Regulations, addressing crucial aspects such as means of warning and escape, internal and external fire spread, and access for the fire service. It provides stakeholders with a transparent overview of building construction, underlying assumptions, and precautionary measures, fostering collaboration and informed decision-making.</span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">The overarching goal of the retrospective fire strategy is to effectively manage, plan, and coordinate fire safety procedures, thereby mitigating fire risks and safeguarding occupant safety. Serving as a cornerstone for fire risk assessments, it guides proactive measures to counter fire hazards and protect both occupants and assets.</span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Key aspects include:</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="../uploads/images/11.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Performance based design</h3>\r\n<p>Desktop Review</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Detailed review of Facility drawings (As built, FLS Strategy, Fire Alarm, firefighting, smoke management drawings), O&amp;M Manuals, &nbsp;Commissioning &amp; &nbsp;CFD Reports etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Building Fire Safety Audit</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Detailed site inspection of Means of egress features, Fire and Life Safety systems, Emergency Systems, Evacuation strategies etc</li>\r\n<li>Cause and Effect testing of FLS Systems.</li>\r\n<li>Gap Analysis Report</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Retrospective Fire &amp; Life Safety Strategy</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Final Retrospective FLS Strategy optimizing minimal changes and ensuring compliance incorporating resilience.</li>\r\n<li>Corrective Actions for achieving retrospective strategy.</li>\r\n<li>AHJ Submissions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/9.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 6, 1, '2025-11-20 09:20:09', '2025-11-21 02:40:23'),
	(6, 1, 'Risk Assessment - Hazardous Materials Storage & Process', 'risk-assessment-hazardous-materials-storage-process', 'Hazardous materials whether stored, processed or transported, present unique fire and life-safety challenges. Our risk assessments evaluate the storage conditions, process flows and potential failure modes to protect people, property and operations. \r\n', '<div class="container py-4">Hazardous materials whether stored, processed or transported, present unique fire and life-safety challenges. Our risk assessments evaluate the storage conditions, process flows and potential failure modes to protect people, property and operations.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; font-weight: bold; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Code Compliance</span></h3>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Ensuring Code Compliance for Hazardous Materials process, storage and handling requires careful planning, Assessments.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">we bring together a multidisciplinary team of Hazardous Materials Specialists, Emergency Response Experts, and Fire Protection Engineers who possess deep knowledge of both regional and international fire safety codes such as NFPA, OSHA, SBC, UAE Fire Code and other local HSE requirements.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><img class="img-fluid rounded" src="../uploads/images/27a.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><img class="img-fluid rounded" src="../uploads/images/32.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; font-weight: bold; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Risk Assessments &amp; Mitigation</span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Both existing and newly developed facilities that manage hazardous materials or critical infrastructure require comprehensive Risk Analysis and Assessment using advanced engineering methodologies. These evaluations are essential to identify potential fire, explosion, and operational hazards, enabling the implementation of effective mitigation strategies that meet the acceptable safety thresholds mandated by Authorities Having Jurisdiction (AHJ).</span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Xeluxe leverages<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>analytical tools, quantitative &amp; qualitative risk assessment models, and performance-based engineering techniques to ensure that every facility operates at the highest level of safety, resilience, and regulatory compliance.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/Marina_1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 5, 1, '2025-11-20 09:22:44', '2025-11-21 02:33:55'),
	(7, 1, 'Peer Review and Authority Representation', 'peer-review-and-authority-representation', 'Our experienced team has engaged in Mega projects across the regions and is versatile in developing Fire and Life safety strategies as per international standards viz International Building Code, International Fire Code, NFPA standards, British Standards - Approved Document B, BS 9999, BS 7974, along with local codes such as Saudi Building code, UAE Fire and Life Safety Code, and GCC Codes. \r\n', '<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; font-weight: bold; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Code Compliant Fire &amp; Life Safety Design</span></h3>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Our experienced team has engaged in Mega projects across the regions and is versatile in developing Fire and Life safety strategies as per international standards viz International Building Code, International Fire Code, NFPA standards, British Standards - Approved Document B, BS 9999, BS 7974, along with local codes such as Saudi Building code, UAE Fire and Life Safety Code, and GCC Codes. </span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">Our holistic approach assists our clients in streamlining the design at the early stages as per code and authority requirements. The Organization places emphasis on providing practical solutions to upkeep the uniqueness of the design while maintaining the intent of the code. </span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Century Gothic\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Aptos; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; language: en-GB; mso-style-textfill-type: solid; mso-style-textfill-fill-themecolor: text1; mso-style-textfill-fill-color: black; mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha: 100.0%;">The Organization possess affiliation with UAE and Saudi Civil D&eacute;fense Administrations and are authorized to endorse Fire and Life Safety submissions to the Authority Having jurisdiction. </span></p>\r\n<p style="language: en-AE; line-height: 115%; margin-top: 12.0pt; margin-bottom: 8.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><img class="img-fluid rounded" src="../uploads/images/36.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row g-4">\r\n<div class="col-md-3 text-center">\r\n<h5><img src="../uploads/images/civil-defence-dubai.png" alt="" width="100%"></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 text-center">\r\n<h5><img src="../uploads/images/iso.png" alt="" width="100%"></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 text-center">\r\n<h5><img src="../uploads/images/nfpa-cfps.png" alt="" width="100%"></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 text-center">\r\n<h5><img src="../uploads/images/sfpe.png" alt="" width="100%"></h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/29.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 4, 1, '2025-11-20 09:25:47', '2025-11-21 02:30:39'),
	(8, 1, 'Emergency Response Planning', 'emergency-response-planning', 'We develop comprehensive emergency preparedness plans that equip organizations with the tools, training, and strategies needed to respond swiftly, minimize disruption, and restore operations with minimal impact.\r\n', '<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row align-items-center">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<h4>Emergency Preparedness: A Critical Pillar of Safety and Resilience</h4>\r\n<p>Effective emergency preparedness is essential to ensure a rapid, coordinated, and efficient response during fire and life safety incidents. It not only helps protect lives and assets in the immediate term but also plays a vital role in business continuity and post-incident recovery.</p>\r\n<p>We develop comprehensive emergency preparedness plans that equip organizations with the tools, training, and strategies needed to respond swiftly, minimize disruption, and restore operations with minimal impact.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Developing the right Framework suited for your Organization</h3>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li>Emergency Preparedness plans developed through collaboration and understanding the needs of the Organization and regulatory requirements.</li>\r\n<li>Integrated with Organization&rsquo;s hierarchy and Security protocols.<br>&uuml;Building Emergency Response Plans</li>\r\n<li>Evacuation Layouts</li>\r\n<li>Pre Incident Plans catering to credible scenarios</li>\r\n<li>Emergency Response Trainings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="../uploads/images/27b.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3>Emergency Response Force planning &amp; Fire Station Design</h3>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li>Emergency Response Force development in alignment with Masterplan needs</li>\r\n<li>Experienced support for Fire Station design</li>\r\n<li>Emergency Response Planning &amp; resource allocation studies</li>\r\n<li>Supports Public and Private Fire brigades</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img src="../uploads/images/29.jpg" alt="" width="100%"></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/29.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 8, 1, '2025-11-20 09:28:22', '2025-11-21 02:55:28'),
	(9, 2, 'Process Safety', 'process-safety', 'Our Process Safety expertise spans a diverse range of disciplines, including technical HSE, process safety management, hazard identification and analysis, loss prevention strategies, risk assessment and mitigation, and compliance with international safety standards. ', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our Process Safety expertise spans a diverse range of disciplines, including technical HSE, process safety management, hazard identification and analysis, loss prevention strategies, risk assessment and mitigation, and compliance with international safety standards. We specialize in delivering comprehensive solutions for the Oil &amp; Gas sector across offshore and onshore, upstream, and downstream process industries.</p>\r\n<p>Our team comprises highly qualified professionals with extensive experience in process safety management, hazard analysis, and risk assessment. Their deep understanding of industryImage standards, combined with hands-on expertise in complex projects, ensures the delivery of practical and effective safety solutions. Leveraging cutting-edge tools and methodologies, our personnel are dedicated to maintaining operational safety, regulatory compliance, and asset integrity across all project phases.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row g-4">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">HAZID/HAZOP Studies</h5>\r\n<p class="card-text">+ Technical HSE Studies<br>+ HAZID/ HAZOP Studies<br>+ SIL, LOPA, Bow-Tie Analysis</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Consequence Modelling</h5>\r\n<p class="card-text">+ Consequence modelling of gas dispersion, fire and explosion using software like PHAST.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Quantitative Risk Assessment</h5>\r\n<p class="card-text">+ QRA Studies<br>+ FERA Studies<br>+ MAHM Studies</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/27a.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2025-11-20 09:45:19', '2025-11-21 03:25:34'),
	(10, 3, 'Engineering Simulations', 'engineering-simulations', 'Our design team has extensive experience in performance-based options with major architects and in iconic projects and has resolved limitations posed by code requirements by effectively justifying that the code intent is met by achieving specific fire and life safety goals.    \r\n', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Performance based design provides equivalent means of compliance where the complex and sophisticated architecture, as in modern day projects, demands flexibility beyond prescriptive code compliance. Our design team has extensive experience in performance-based options with major architects and in iconic projects and has resolved limitations posed by code requirements by effectively justifying that the code intent is met by achieving specific fire and life safety goals.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row g-4">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Fire Modelling and Smoke Analysis</h5>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li class="card-text">Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD)Analysis of smoke movement using FDS/ FLUENT and evaluating tenability.</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Optimizing Smoke Control systems.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Egress and Crowd Movement simulation</h5>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li class="card-text">Computer Aided Analysis of occupant evacuation (Pathfinder)</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Alternative compliance in travel distances and higher Occupant Load</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">ASET vs RSET Analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Structural Analysis</h5>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li class="card-text">Analysis of structures in fire conditions.</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Finite Element Analysis</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Alternative compliance in structural fire rating.</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Value Engineering</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row g-4">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Thermal Comfort Analysis</h5>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li class="card-text">CFD Analysis for thermal comfort</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Hourly Analysis Program (HAP)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Chiller Yard and Cooling Tower Performance Analysis</h5>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li>Heat rejection simulation and analysis</li>\r\n<li>Equipment performance analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Tunnel &amp; Car Park Ventilation</h5>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li class="card-text">Tunnel Fire strategy, CFD and Ventilation analysis</li>\r\n<li class="card-text">Car Park Ventilation Analysis and CFD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/10.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2025-11-20 09:46:35', '2025-11-21 03:32:21'),
	(11, 4, 'Acoustics', 'acoustics', 'Our Acoustics services focus on creating sound environments that enhance occupant comfort. By addressing both architectural and mechanical acoustics, we ensure that spaces are designed not only for functionality but also for optimal acoustic performance, contributing to overall well-being and satisfaction.', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our Acoustics services focus on creating sound environments that enhance occupant comfort. By addressing both architectural and mechanical acoustics, we ensure that spaces are designed not only for functionality but also for optimal acoustic performance, contributing to overall well-being and satisfaction.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container py-4">\r\n<div class="row g-4">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Architectural Acoustics</h5>\r\n<p class="card-text">We provide consulting services in architectural acoustics to enhance sound quality and minimize noise disruptions within buildings. Our approach involves analyzing materials, design, and layout to achieve optimal acoustic performance, ensuring a comfortable and conducive environment for occupants.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">MEP Acoustics</h5>\r\n<p class="card-text">Our expertise in mechanical, electrical, and plumbing (MEP) acoustics ensures that these systems operate quietly and do not negatively impact the building\'s overall acoustic environment. We focus on soundproofing and noise control to enhance occupant comfort.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="card border shadow-sm h-100">\r\n<div class="card-body">\r\n<h5 class="card-title">Industrial &amp; Environmental Acoustics</h5>\r\n<p class="card-text">We assess and mitigate noise pollution in industrial settings and environmental contexts. Our services help clients comply with regulatory requirements while ensuring that noise levels do not adversely affect the working environment and the surrounding communities as well. This includes conducting noise studies and recommending effective sound control solutions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/21b.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2025-11-20 09:47:43', '2025-11-21 03:34:22'),
	(12, 6, 'Construction Supervision', 'construction-supervision', 'We provide comprehensive construction supervision services across architecture, structure, infrastructure, MEP, FLS and ICT. Our role is to ensure that every phase of construction aligns with the approved design, technical standards, and contractual requirements.\r\n', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We provide comprehensive construction supervision services across architecture, structure, infrastructure, MEP, FLS and ICT. Our role is to ensure that every phase of construction aligns with the approved design, technical standards, and contractual requirements.</p>\r\n<p>A common challenge in the industry is the disconnect that arises when design and supervision are managed by separate consultants. This often leads to design gaps, insufficient detail, or unclear documentation - issues that can result in delays and additional costs during execution.</p>\r\n<p>Our construction supervision methodology addresses this by incorporating independent peer review as a core service. This allows us to critically assess design documents before and during construction, helping to identify inconsistencies and improve constructability.</p>\r\n<p>While some may advocate for combining design and supervision under one consultant, we believe an independent, third-party perspective better serves the client&rsquo;s interest. It ensures objectivity, promotes accountability, and strengthens overall project delivery.</p>\r\n<p>Our role extends beyond monitoring compliance&mdash;we provide an additional layer of quality assurance that supports informed decision-making, reduces risk, and helps deliver successful project outcomes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/1.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2025-11-20 09:49:07', '2025-11-21 03:35:00'),
	(13, 5, 'Commissioning', 'commissioning', 'Our team ensures that building systems - particularly MEP and Fire Life Safety (FLS) - are designed, installed, tested, and performing in accordance with the design intent. At its core, commissioning is a process of communication, documentation, and verification - bringing together stakeholders to ensure the building operates as it was envisioned.\r\n', '<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-12">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our team ensures that building systems - particularly MEP and Fire Life Safety (FLS) - are designed, installed, tested, and performing in accordance with the design intent. At its core, commissioning is a process of communication, documentation, and verification - bringing together stakeholders to ensure the building operates as it was envisioned.</p>\r\n<p>A common challenge in the industry is the lack of accurate and complete documentation, including as-built drawings, test records, and O&amp;M manuals. This often hampers effective building operation and long-term maintenance. Our approach places strong emphasis on documentation quality and handover readiness, ensuring that all commissioning records and system information are complete, verifiable, and aligned with actual site conditions.</p>\r\n<p>Our commissioning services include:</p>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\r\n<li>Commissioning Agent &ndash; Independent oversight to verify that systems meet performance requirements through structured testing and review.</li>\r\n<li>Commissioning Management &ndash; End-to-end coordination of commissioning activities, documentation, and stakeholder communication to ensure a streamlined process.</li>\r\n<li>Re-Commissioning &ndash; Restoring systems in previously commissioned buildings that no longer operate at intended performance levels.</li>\r\n<li>Retro-Commissioning &ndash; Improving functionality and efficiency in existing buildings that were never formally commissioned.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Across all services, our role extends beyond compliance - we provide a final layer of performance assurance, ensuring systems operate as intended and the client receives a fully optimized asset.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'uploads/images/7.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'summary_large_image', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, '2025-11-20 09:50:07', '2025-11-21 03:37:05');
